Class SiotNetGatewayManagerWear

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.siot.android.gateway.SiotNetGatewayManagerWear

  • public class SiotNetGatewayManagerWear
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Sathesh Paramasamy on 28.11.15. siot.net gateway library SiotNetGatewayManagerWear. Use to connect the android wear device through the mobile to the siot.net and using the sensorservice correctly configured.
